{"tid":2330823,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"洛歇．馬丁將參與三菱重工所領導的F-3研發計畫","createTime":"2020-12-18T10:06:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-18T11:20:14.000Z","uid":75656,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"38285eb59ea1b12911844cee386f95afd3aeac47","tid":2330823,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T10:06:42.000Z","msg":"為讓日本全新世代匿蹤戰機與美方擁有較好互相操作性，日本防衛省今天（18日）宣佈，洛克希德&middot;馬丁將參與日本三菱重工業（Mitsubishi Heavy Industries）領導的F-3戰鬥機研製計畫，預計2030年代中期展開服役，作為F-2戰機的後繼機種。<br />\n<br />\n據《路透》報導，日本防衛省今天（18日）在記者會上透露，洛馬將參與三菱重工所領導的研發計畫，重建30年前研製F-2戰機時的夥伴關係。而F-3戰鬥機定於2030年代中期進入日本防衛省航空自衛隊服役，以跟上中國飛機技術發展的腳步。<br />\n<br />\n《路透》指出，<span class=\"red\">日本防衛省說，「為了要確保與美國的互相操作性，我們將從明年開始共同開展此計畫」</span>，全新世代的匿蹤戰機F-3戰機亦為F-X戰機計畫，預計將耗資400億美元（約新台幣1.13兆元）研製，用以取代F-2戰機。<span class=\"red\">洛馬先前提出了混合F-22戰機與F-35戰機的設計規劃，不過遭到日本回絕，因為日方比較想用採用本土設計。</span><br />\n<br />\n為了要降低F-3戰機的研發成本，日本表示會持續尋求美方與英國的合作，取得技術。<span class=\"red\">除了洛馬，其他國外公司也不斷表示有興趣要參與F-3戰機的發展計畫，包含美國波音公司（Boeing Co）與諾斯洛普&middot;格魯曼 （Northrop Grumman Corp）公司，前者為F-18「超級大黃蜂」戰機製造商，另外，還有英國貝宜系統（BAE Systems Plc）與引擎製造商勞斯萊斯（Rolls-Royce Holdings Plc）等。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3385329\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3385329&d=PGKZrCzpIeFm7bz4D1EKrYlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=4210306b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3385329&h=d0533821\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3385329</a><br />\n<br />\n路透社：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/idUSKBN28S0N6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2FidUSKBN28S0N6&d=PGKZrCzpIeFm7bz4D1EKrYlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=4a3a25b3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2FidUSKBN28S0N6&h=e2977520\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/article/idUSKBN28S0N6</a>"},{"pid":"427fc1def962dbedd1088950a595c43ddc08dee0","tid":2330823,"uid":48531,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T10:07:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71ffbb9d33a8779e87da9141e6c1cc36e55f741d","tid":2330823,"uid":121146,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T10:09:28.000Z","msg":"消息人士指China Joke表示中國會唔開心  上台後會腰斬計畫"},{"pid":"213106ae760f637bc22cc3d697e9008911cfdb66","tid":2330823,"uid":19287,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T10:11:49.000Z","msg":"F-2事件翻版？"},{"pid":"a694de1cf81dc9432a701e3e1cd94b99556c4c19","tid":2330823,"uid":231102,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T10:20:03.000Z","msg":"聽講Boeing同Lockheed Martin都被支共制裁，<br />\n唔知支共點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8da2bfa6a58186ea07cb47172df7c6a0570ea9e8","tid":2330823,"uid":271807,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T10:23:15.000Z","msg":"強強聯手"},{"pid":"b65c2ebe34f2689cd877ac1529fe12e81983b61d","tid":2330823,"uid":70487,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a694de1cf81dc9432a701e3e1cd94b99556c4c19","tid":2330823,"uid":231102,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T10:20:03.000Z","msg":"聽講Boeing同Lockheed Martin都被支共制裁，<br />\n唔知支共點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T10:23:23.000Z","msg":"今次真係痾拔甩"},{"pid":"7214aa0f9d34b8b1d0d5224780103d7986ec9a74","tid":2330823,"uid":63543,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"213106ae760f637bc22cc3d697e9008911cfdb66","tid":2330823,"uid":19287,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T10:11:49.000Z","msg":"F-2事件翻版？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T10:31:43.000Z","msg":"f2發生咩事？"},{"pid":"d19aa590dcb57090665f